Ender,

As a workaround, you should be able to use &#39;pure_solid&#39;. But a much 
better answer is that in the next release you will be able to work with 
several pure fluids with built-in accurate liquid/vapor equations of 
state.  Water is one of these, along with hydrogen, nitrogen, oxygen, 
methane, and HFC-134a.  I hope to have it ready by the end of this week 
or early next week.

Dave


